data.description: 3/2 split plan concrete block home in the up and coming area of Silver Springs Shores.  House was built in 2019 and all is original with no issues. Home had a fresh coat of paint done on the interior just a week ago along with all the doors being repainted.  Don’t miss out on this cozy home perfect for a growing family or first time home buyers!
